phone - The user's phone number.
address - The user's address.
active - True if the user is active.
agencyName - The name of the agency this user belongs to.
notifyOnWarnings - True if we should notify this user of harvester warnings.
notifyOnChagnes - True if we should notify this user of changes to objects they own.
